{
  "stem": "13395.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think that this SS man maybe had a son on the front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And maybe he didn't hear from him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And maybe he was waiting for a letter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe that's why I'm alive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You never know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so that was my episode with sending a letter to my mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- we knew that there was other camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But let me tell you first, so we don't lose the, the continuity of the story.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "While we were-- I was in camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister was in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In June of 1942, they deported the whole ghetto of Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother found herself with my father and with her in-laws, with my grandmother and her husband, on the truck to be shipped to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "By coincidence with the parents of my friends, with the two girls that we were together, and while waiting for the convoy to move, the mother of my friend said to my mother, if-- I hope we all survive.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in case I don't, would you be a mother to my children?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you wouldn't survive and I do, I will do the same for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Among the screams and cries, mothers looking for the children, babies being tossed around, people being beaten, old people not being able to get on those trucks, in that whole confusion, in that whole tragedy that was unfolding, it got a little dark.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They came to an end.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother pushed my father off the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She jumped after him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they ran away and hid in the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The convoys left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Jaworzno.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The convoy left with the people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "With my father's mother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He left her behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were situations, these were decisions that Jews had to make.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
